'''''Star Wars: The Official Magazine'' 47''', also styled as '''''Star Wars'' Magazine 47''',  was the 47th issue of the ''[[Star Wars: The Official Magazine]]''. It primarily reprinted content from [[Star Wars Insider 67|''Star Wars Insider'' 67]].

==Contents==
*Cover Story - Jedi's Lost Scenes
*"[[The Ultimate Return of the Jedi Insider's Guide|The Ultimate ''Return of the Jedi'' Insider's Guide]]" {{C|from [[Star Wars Insider 67|''Star Wars Insider'' 67]]}}
*"[[FX Karma: Pickle Ships, Tennis Shoes, and Other Untold Tales of the Return of the Jedi Space Battle|FX Karma: Pickle Ships, Tennis Shoes, and Other Untold Tales of the ''Return of the Jedi'' Space Battle]]" {{C|from ''Star Wars Insider'' 67}}
*"[[Beyond the Valley of the Ewoks]]" {{C|from ''Star Wars Insider'' 67}}
*"[[Seeking Revenge: A Collector's History of Revenge of the Jedi|Seeking Revenge: A Collector's History of ''Revenge of the Jedi'']]" {{C|from ''Star Wars Insider'' 67}}
*"[[The Trouble with Squibs]]" {{C|from ''Star Wars Insider'' 67}}
*"[[Insider Interview|''Insider'' Interview: Lama Su]]" {{C|from ''Star Wars Insider'' 67}}
